    "body": "<span class=\"solution-visible-txt\">All submissions for this problem are available.</span><p>\u00a0</p>\n<p>Given the values of A,D,N and X.<br />\nFind the value of the following expression:</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://latex.codecogs.com/gif.latex?\\sum_{i=0}^{n}(A+i*D)*(X^{N-i})\" title=\"\\sum_{i=1}^{n}(A+i*d)*(x^{N-i})\" /></p>\n<p>Since the answer can be very large,output the final answer % 274877906944.</p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<pre>First line will contain T,the no of test cases.\nThe next T lines will contain the values of A,D,N,X.</pre><p><b>Note: For this problem submissions are allowed only in C/C++</b></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p>For each test case output the required answer in a single line.</p>\n<h3>Constraints</h3>\n<p>1&lt;=T&lt;=100</p>\n<p>0&lt;=A,D,X&lt;=10^5</p>\n<p>0&lt;=N&lt;=10^6</p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<pre><b>Input: \n</b>\n2\n1 1 1 1\n2 2 2 2\n\n<b>Output:</b>\n3\n22\n\n</pre><p>\u00a0</p>\n",
